version_description: This tab is based on live versions of the song. The song is played without a capo and is how Win Butler plays the acoustic guitar part.
An easier for beginners to playing key
Has intro in the chord sheet, and there are a few corrections with this version like capo placement and chord that were missed.

Broken down piece by piece so that, with a little time and effort, you can play exactly like the recording. This comprehensive version includes tabs, chords and all the strumming patterns you'll need to play just like Kaleo.
Acoustic version with fingerstyle picking. Capo on 1st fret, standard tuning.
